---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import HitCounter from '../components/HitCounter.astro';
---

<Page title="alexander campos" description="I build tools and write about how systems model people. Shipped products, essays on observation and identity.">
  <section class="splash">
    <h1 class="site-name">Alexander Campos</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Mostly interested in how systems model people - and what happens when people can see the model.</p>
    <p class="warm-line">you are at the front door.</p>

    <div class="retro-marquee-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="retro-marquee-text">
        <a href="https://reframed.works" style="color: var(--gold-accent); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: none;">reframed.works — live</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;playing like it pays · building like it's clay — NoVA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://reframed.works" style="color: var(--gold-accent); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: none;">reframed.works — live</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;playing like it pays · building like it's clay — NoVA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- what I build -->
  <section class="home-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">what I build</h2>

    <div class="project-cards">
      <a href="/projects/reframed" class="project-card">
        <span class="project-name">Reframed</span>
        <span class="project-line">Helps people describe their experience honestly and still get the job. Live at <span class="gold">reframed.works</span>.</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/projects/forgeframe" class="project-card">
        <span class="project-name">ForgeFrame</span>
        <span class="project-line">Open-source memory for agents. Memories decay over time. Principles don't. You decide which is which.</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/projects/guardian" class="project-card">
        <span class="project-name">Guardian</span>
        <span class="project-line">Desktop control plane for inference. Sits at the boundary between you and the model - scrubs what shouldn't leave, injects what should arrive.</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="more-link"><a href="/projects">all projects >></a></p>
  </section>

  <!-- what I think -->
  <section class="home-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">what I think</h2>

    <div class="essay-cards">
      <a href="/writing/on-observation-and-identity-modeling" class="essay-card">
        <span class="essay-title">On Observation and Identity Modeling</span>
        <span class="essay-line">How systems build models of the people who use them - and what happens when the model starts shaping the person.</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/writing/where-the-difference-is-stored" class="essay-card">
        <span class="essay-title">Where the Difference Is Stored</span>
        <span class="essay-line">The loop became measurable. Three substrates, three methods, one question: what do you put on the other side of it?</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="more-link"><a href="/writing">all writing >></a></p>
  </section>

  <!-- what I can do for you -->
  <section class="home-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">if you need something built</h2>

    <p class="home-prose">
      Sites, search visibility, and the infrastructure that makes a business findable.
    </p>

    <div class="service-row">
      <a href="/audit" class="service-pill">free site audit</a>
      <a href="/services" class="service-pill">all services</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- the short version -->
  <section class="home-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">the short version</h2>
    <p class="home-prose dim">
      The <a href="/resume">resume</a> has the history. The <a href="https://github.com/notaprompt">repos</a> have the code. <a href="mailto:alex@campos.works">Get in touch</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="counter-row">
      <HitCounter />
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    console.log(
      '%c you are at the front door -- again, kinda. ',
      'color: #b8965a; font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px;'
    );
  </script>

  <script is:inline src="/islands/hit-counter.js"></script>
</Page>

<style>
  /* ── Opening ── */
  .splash {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .site-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--glow);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--glow);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .warm-line {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--white-30);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  /* ── Sections ── */
  .home-section {
    padding: 1.75rem 0 0.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--white-04);
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--white-20);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .home-prose {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--white-60);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  .home-prose.dim { color: var(--white-30); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; }

  .home-prose a {
    color: var(--white-70);
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--white-20);
  }

  .home-prose a:hover {
    color: var(--gold-accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--gold-accent);
  }

  .more-link {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .more-link a {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--gold-accent);
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .more-link a:hover { color: var(--glow-hot); }

  /* ── Project cards ── */
  .project-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--white-08);
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .project-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold-accent); }

  .project-name {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--glow);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .project-line {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--white-45);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .gold { color: var(--gold-accent); }

  /* ── Essay cards ── */
  .essay-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .essay-card {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--white-08);
    padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .essay-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold-accent); }

  .essay-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--glow);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .essay-line {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--white-45);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── Services row ── */
  .service-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-pill {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--gold-accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-accent);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }

  .service-pill:hover {
    background: var(--gold-accent);
    color: var(--void);
  }

  /* ── Counter ── */
  .counter-row {
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--white-04);
  }

  /* ── Mobile ── */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .service-row { flex-direction: column; }
    .service-pill { text-align: center; }
  }

  /* ── Pixel Grid Hover Texture ── */
  @media (hover: hover) {
    .project-card:hover, .essay-card:hover {
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='2' height='2' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Crect width='1' height='1' fill='white' fill-opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      background-size: 2px 2px;
    }
  }
</style>
